description: Truck 54 is a food truck serving the Tucson area with delicious food while supporting a great mission: to provide employment opportunities for individuals recovering from mental illness. During their time in job-training and on the truck, these individuals are taught work skills, encouraged to develop their own natural abilities, and learn to believe in themselves.On the food side, the truck offers tasty bistro meals reflecting the menu served at Cafe 54 - soups, salads, and sandwiches in both meat and vegetarian options.If you're hungry for food and hungry to enact positive change within your community, there's no better lunch stop for you than Truck 54, so visit today!
name: Truck 54
